#CircuitBreakerSG D-31
Our one-dish Vegetarian Braised Yee Fu noodle on Vesak Day. Throw in some simple ingredients like homegrown Beansprout, Baby Bok Choy and scrambled egg white (leftover from making Blueberry Tarts). Sprinkle with some homemade crispy Shallot.

Enjoy your lunch & the rest of the day!
